description:
This week on Unqualified, Anna and Sim welcome the incredibly talented, Golden Globe winning actress, Maura Tierney (NewsRadio, ER, The Affair)!

Maura brings her acting chops and intellect to the table as her and Anna engage in some stimulating conversation about…

  • The ins-and-outs of being an actor
  • Whorehouses, stud farms, and Heidi Fleiss
  • Maura’s volunteer experience in Greece

Next, the ladies jump into an Unqualified game where Maura weighs-in on dating professions like…

  • A brew-master
  • A psychotherapist with a stand-up comedy side-gig
  • A professional poker player
  • A truck driver with a pension for exercising at rest stops
  • A restaurant manager

On the phones this week…

  • Amanda, 30, from Chicago needs some advice on how to cope with being left out of a trip to Iceland that her husband is taking with his siblings and their spouses while Amanda is stuck at home with the kids.

 

  • Michelle, 31, from San Francisco has an Instagram dating dilemma involving a high school guy that she has reconnected with and is interested in, but she isn’t sure how long to wait for him to ask her out before moving on.

 

Follow us!

Anna Faris: @annakfaris

Unqualified: @unqualified
